			      C     ; Stage two stays in a single tiny-model segment: code, data, and the IRQ1
			      C     ; handler all expect DS = CS. SS:SP still points at the inherited bootstrap
			      C     ; stack, while FS stays reserved for the enhanced flat-memory presenter.
